        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>This liquid contains blood from a silver dragon. For 1 hour after you imbibe the concoction, you can unleash a silver dragon's breath weapon. The potency of the breath depends on the potion's type, based on the age of the dragon whose blood was used to make the potion.</p>\n<p>Exhaling dragon breath uses a single action. You create a 15-foot cone of cold which deals 6d6 cold damage. All creatures in the area must attempt a DC 29 basic Reflex save.</p>\n<p>After you use the breath weapon, you can't do so again for 1d4 rounds.</p>"
